What you need to know:

Faith is in form this season, having clocked a best of 1:58.26 in the 800m at the Doha Diamond League meet last month.Robert Kiprop will be the sole Kenyan in the 5,000m race, which has favourite Uganda’s Joshua Cheptegei, Ethiopia’s Edris Muktar, siblings Jakob Ingebrigtsen and Henrik Ingebrigtsen from Norway among others.